OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1776258665
OL,3,CCouncil scraps plans to close three
OL,4,Cfire stations following public outcry
OL,6,FPlans to close three fire stations in
OL,7,FOxfordshire have been scrapped
OL,8,Ffollowing a public consultation.
OL,10,FOxfordshire County Council had been
OL,11,Fconsidering closing its sites in
OL,12,FEynsham, Henley and Woodstock, due to
OL,13,Flow availability of on-call crews.
OL,15,FThe plans had prompted outrage from
OL,16,Fthe Fire Brigades Union which had
OL,17,Fdescribed them as 'dangerous' and a
OL,18,Fthread to public safety. It has
OL,19,Fwelcomed the councils decision to
OL,20,Fcancel them.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/8
