PN,41802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1776258665
OL,3,CCouncil scraps plans to close three
OL,4,Cfire stations following public outcry
OL,6,FThe council says residents' feedback
OL,7,Fmade it clear how important local fire
OL,8,Fstations are with communities showing
OL,9,Fstrong support for retaining them,
OL,10,Fhence the change of course.
OL,12,FThe main proposal in the public
OL,13,Fconsultation was to address what the
OL,14,Fauthority described as 'ongoing
OL,15,Fchallenges with fire engine
OL,16,Favailability during the daytime'.
OL,17,FDemand and risk are highest during the
OL,18,Fdaytime, the council added.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
