FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1776258665
OL,3,CCouncil scraps plans to close three
OL,4,Cfire stations following public outcry
OL,6,FWork will now focus on ensuring
OL,7,FOxfordshire Fire and Rescue Service
OL,8,Fcan deliver its key objectives of
OL,9,Fimproved first response times,
OL,10,Fincreased daytime cover, stronger
OL,11,Fservice resilience, and an increased
OL,12,Famount of fire prevention work.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
