PN,41804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1776258665
OL,3,CCouncil scraps plans to close three
OL,4,Cfire stations following public outcry
OL,6,FRob MacDougall, Oxfordshire County
OL,7,FCouncil Fire and Rescue Service's
OL,8,FChief Fire Officer, said: "I'd like to
OL,9,Fthank everyone who shared their views
OL,10,Fon our proposals during the public
OL,11,Fconsultation. We received over a
OL,12,Fthousand responses, and it was
OL,13,Fimportant that we listened carefully
OL,14,Fto what people told us.
OL,16,F"It's important that we regularly
OL,17,Freview our resources and work closely
OL,18,Fwith our local communities and
OL,19,Fcolleagues to gain consensus on how
OL,20,Fbest to shape the service to meet
OL,21,Fcurrent and future needs.
OL,26,@pD@[OUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
