OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1776258665
OL,3,CCouncil scraps plans to close three
OL,4,Cfire stations following public outcry
OL,6,F"It's apparent, having read and
OL,7,Flistened to those who gave us their
OL,8,Ffeedback, that local people are keen
OL,9,Fto support existing fire stations in
OL,10,Ftheir towns and villages.
OL,12,F"Building on that community support,
OL,13,Fwe'll be taking revised proposals to
OL,14,FOxfordshire County Council's cabinet
OL,15,Fon 21 April, which will include
OL,16,Freviewing and adapting our recruitment
OL,17,Fcampaigns at Eynsham, Henley and
OL,18,FWoodstock, with the aim of increasing
OL,19,Fon-call firefighter numbers and
OL,20,Fimproving fire engine availability."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOU|D@dO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/8
