PN,41806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1776258665
OL,3,CCouncil scraps plans to close three
OL,4,Cfire stations following public outcry
OL,6,FOxfordshire County Council also
OL,7,Fconfirmed it will work with the Fire
OL,8,FBrigades Union to improve the service.
OL,10,FThe U-turn has been welcomed by the
OL,11,Funion, which led a campaign to stop
OL,12,Fthe cuts.
OL,14,FFire Brigades Union general secretary
OL,15,FSteve Wright said: "This climbdown on
OL,16,Fstation closures and cuts is a
OL,17,Ftestimony to the power of collective
OL,18,Faction through the Fire Brigades Union.
OL,26,@wD@TOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1776258665
OL,3,CCouncil scraps plans to close three
OL,4,Cfire stations following public outcry
OL,6,F"A massive vote in favour of strike
OL,7,Faction by our members made plain the
OL,8,Fstrength of feeling among firefighters
OL,9,Fabout cuts to the service that
OL,10,Fthreaten the lives of firefighters and
OL,11,Fthe public.
OL,13,F"These proposals would have slashed
OL,14,Ffire cover across the county, putting
OL,15,Flives at risk. Thanks to the
OL,16,Fdetermination and unity of our
OL,17,Fmembers, those cuts have now been
OL,18,Fstopped.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/8
